headline: Will Woodford Reserve Double Double Oaked Relaunch Change Brown-Forman's (BF.B) Premiumization Narrative?
summary: Earlier this week, Brown-Forman announced the nationwide return of Woodford Reserve Double Double Oaked Bourbon, a highly sought-after expression that has long attracted strong interest from American whiskey enthusiasts. This re-release highlights how Brown-Forman can still galvanize consumer excitement around premium, limited-style offerings even as analysts voice concerns about broader demand headwinds. We’ll now explore how the nationwide Double Double Oaked relaunch interacts with...
